room_title: Escape room "Criminal Capture - the Zodiac Killer" by Axxiom Escape Rooms Wilmington in Wilmington (DE)
room_description: Criminal Capture is our new series of fully immersed crimes that need to be solved. Your team is a part of the behavioral analysis unit and you are tasked with acquiring the necessary information, analyzing the evidence and thwarting the next crime in order to catch the criminal!
